    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really well-loved over the years. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it just as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
