      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it. It runs super smoothly and has been well-taken care of over the years. Perfect if you\u2019re looking for a reliable ride that won\u2019t break the bank. I'd love for it to go to a good home\u2014come check it out and take it for a spin!",
