      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six provides exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS system. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a factory limited-slip differential. The cooling system has been recently overhauled, and the critical rear subframe reinforcement has been professionally completed to ensure chassis rigidity. Suspension geometry remains true with refreshed control arm bushings and dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the drivetrain is robust and the valvetrain is quiet, making this a quintessential analog performance machine for the discerning purist.",
